  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0001",
          "zh": "耶律化哥耶律斡臘耶律速撒蕭阿魯帶耶律那也耶律何魯掃古耶律世良",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0002",
          "zh": "耶律斡臘，字斯寧，奚叠剌部人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0003",
          "zh": "趫捷有力，善騎射。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0004",
          "zh": "保寧初，補護衛。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0005",
          "zh": "車駕獵頡山，適豪豬伏叢莽，帝射中，豬突出。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0006",
          "zh": "禦者托滿舍轡而避，廄人鶴骨翼之，斡臘復射而斃。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0007",
          "zh": "帝嘉賞。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0008",
          "zh": "及獵赤山，適奔鹿奮角突前，路隘不容避，垂犯蹕。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0009",
          "zh": "斡臘以身當之，鹿觸而顛。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0010",
          "zh": "帝謂曰：「朕因獵，兩瀕於危，賴卿以免，始見爾心。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0011",
          "zh": "」遷護衛太保。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0012",
          "zh": "從樞密使耶律斜軫破宋將楊繼業軍於山西。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0013",
          "zh": "統和十三年秋，為行軍都監，從都部署奚王和朔奴伐兀惹烏昭度，數月至其城。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0014",
          "zh": "昭度請降。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0015",
          "zh": "和朔奴利其俘掠，令四面急攻。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0016",
          "zh": "昭度率眾死守，隨方捍禦。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0017",
          "zh": "依埤堄虛構戰棚，誘我軍登陴，俄撤枝柱，登者盡覆。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0018",
          "zh": "和朔奴知不能下，欲退。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0019",
          "zh": "蕭恒德謂師久無功，何以藉口，若深入大掠，猶勝空返。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0020",
          "zh": "斡臘曰：「深入，恐所得不償所損。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0021",
          "zh": "」恒德不從，略地東南，循高麗北鄙還。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0022",
          "zh": "道遠糧絕，人馬多死。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0023",
          "zh": "詔奪諸將官，惟斡臘以前議得免。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0024",
          "zh": "尋加同政事門下平章事，為東京留守。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0025",
          "zh": "開泰中卒。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0026",
          "zh": "耶律速撒，字阿敏，性忠直簡毅，練武事。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0027",
          "zh": "應歷初，為侍從，累遷突呂不部節度使。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0028",
          "zh": "歷霸、濟、祥、順、聖五州都總管，俄為敦睦宮太師。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0029",
          "zh": "保寧三年，改九部都詳穩。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0030",
          "zh": "四年，伐党項，屢立戰功，手詔勞之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0031",
          "zh": "統和初，皇太后稱制，西邊甫定，速撒務安集諸蕃，利害輒具以聞，太后益信任之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0032",
          "zh": "凡臨戎，與士卒同甘苦，所獲均賜將校。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0033",
          "zh": "賞順討逆，威信大振。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0034",
          "zh": "在邊二十年卒。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0035",
          "zh": "那也為人廉介，長於理民，每有鬥訟，親核曲直，不尚威嚴，常曰：「凡治人，本欲分別是非，何事迫脅以立名。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0036",
          "zh": "」胡所至以惠化稱。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0037",
          "zh": "耶律何魯掃古，字烏古鄰，孟父房之後。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0038",
          "zh": "重熙末，補祗候郎君。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0039",
          "zh": "清寧初，加安州團練使。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0040",
          "zh": "大康中，歷懷德軍節度使、奚六部禿裏太尉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0041",
          "zh": "詔與樞密官措畫東北邊事，改左護衛太保。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0042",
          "zh": "侍上，言多率易，察無他腸，以故上優貸之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0043",
          "zh": "大安八年，知西北路招討使事。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0044",
          "zh": "時邊部耶睹刮等來侵，何魯掃古誘北阻卜酋豪磨古斯攻之，俘獲甚眾，以功加左僕射。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0045",
          "zh": "復討耶睹刮等，誤擊磨古斯，北阻卜由是叛命。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0046",
          "zh": "遣都監張九討之，不克，二室韋與六院部、特滿群牧、宮分等軍俱陷於敵。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0047",
          "zh": "何魯掃古不以實聞，坐是削官，決以大杖。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0048",
          "zh": "壽隆間，累遷惕隱，兼侍中，賜保節功臣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0049",
          "zh": "道宗崩，與宰相耶律儼總山陵事。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0050",
          "zh": "乾統中，致仕，卒。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0051",
          "zh": "耶律世良，小字斡，六院部人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0052",
          "zh": "才敏給，練達國朝典故及世譜。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0053",
          "zh": "上書與族弟敵烈爭嫡庶，帝始識之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0054",
          "zh": "時北院樞密使韓德讓病，帝問：「孰可代卿？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0055",
          "zh": "」德讓曰：「世良可。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0056",
          "zh": "」北院大王耶律室魯復問北院之選，德讓曰：「無出世良。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0057",
          "zh": "」統和末，為北院大王。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0058",
          "zh": "開泰初，因大冊禮，加檢校太尉、同政事門下平章事。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0059",
          "zh": "時邊部拒命，詔北院樞密使耶律化哥將兵，以世良為都監，往禦之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0060",
          "zh": "明年，化哥還，將罷兵，世良上書曰：「化哥以為無事而還，不思師老糧乏，敵人已去，焉能久守？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0061",
          "zh": "若益兵，可克也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0062",
          "zh": "」帝即命化哥益兵，與世良追之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0063",
          "zh": "至安真河，大破而還。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0064",
          "zh": "自是邊境以寧。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0065",
          "zh": "以功王岐，拜北院樞密使。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0066",
          "zh": "三年，命選馬駝於烏古部。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0067",
          "zh": "會敵烈部人夷剌殺其酋長稍瓦而叛，鄰部皆應，攻陷巨母古城。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0068",
          "zh": "世良率兵壓境，遣人招之，降數部，各復故地。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0069",
          "zh": "四年，伐高麗，為副部署。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0070",
          "zh": "都統劉慎行逗留失期，執還京師，世良獨進兵。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0071",
          "zh": "明年，至北都護府，破追兵於郭州。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0072",
          "zh": "以暴疾卒。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0073",
          "zh": "論曰：大之懷小也以德，制之也以威。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0074",
          "zh": "德不足懷，威不足制，而欲服人也難矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0075",
          "zh": "化哥利俘獲，而諸蕃不附，何魯掃古誤擊磨古斯，而阻卜叛命，是皆喜於一旦之功，而不圖後日之患，庸何議焉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0076",
          "zh": "若斡臘之戒深入，速撒之務安集，亦鐵中之錚錚者邪？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}